---

# 37. What is HashMap?

**Answer:**
Stores data as key-value pairs.

```java
HashMap<Integer,String> map =
new HashMap<>();
```

---

# 38. Difference Between HashMap and Hashtable

| HashMap          | Hashtable    |
| ---------------- | ------------ |
| Not synchronized | Synchronized |
