# 39. What is Garbage Collection?

**Answer:**
Automatic memory cleanup process that removes unused objects from heap memory.

```java
System.gc();
```

---

# 40. What is Multithreading?

**Answer:**
Executing multiple threads simultaneously.

```java
class MyThread extends Thread {

    public void run() {
        System.out.println("Thread Running");
    }
}
```

---

# 41. What is a Package?

**Answer:**
A package is a collection of related classes and interfaces.

```java
package com.company;
```

---

# 42. Access Modifiers in Java

| Modifier  | Access             |
| --------- | ------------------ |
| private   | Same Class         |
| default   | Same Package       |
| protected | Package + Subclass |
| public    | Everywhere         |

---

# 43. What is the Difference Between Heap and Stack Memory?

| Heap           | Stack                  |
| -------------- | ---------------------- |
| Stores Objects | Stores Local Variables |
| Shared Memory  | Thread Specific        |
| Larger         | Smaller                |

